
0. Update gradle.properties/build.gradle
    - for mappings, check https://fabricmc.net/develop
    - update mod properties
        - archives_base_name = generated jar file name
    - fabric_version = check Curseforge for latest version of Fabric API
    - in build.gradle, verify latest Loom with above link
1. Update fabric.mod.json
    - id, version, name, description, authors (if needed), contact, licencse
    - ENTRYPOINTS (super important)
    - mixins if needed
    - depends
    - add suggests if needed
2. Update assets.modid
    - match change folder name to match mod id
    - update modid.mixins.json to match mod id